{"build_type":"executable","description":"LLM read-only lens op.view: render a full .ipm package as its CONCISE form on stdout. Request (argv[1]): {\"view-full-package-as-concise\":{\"path\":\"<ipm>\"}}. Reads the package by path via fetch_request_package_source_bytes (fail-hard read), parses it, and emits the concise object {package, kind, doc?, functions} to stdout. No output file, no stdin. Bad request (no argv, unparseable, no arg object, no/empty/unreadable path, or a file that is not a package — no module_name) -> clean JSON {error}, no crash. Reuses parse_argument_vector_json_request, fetch_request_package_source_bytes, decode_entire_source_building_document, locate_named_member_inside_mapping, render-concise-package-field-entry, vw_all_functions, json-tree-node, add_str_field, emit_result_object_onto_standard_output.","module_name":"render-entire-package-using-concise-representation","package_name":"render-entire-package-using-concise-representation","function_definitions":{"render-entire-package-using-concise-representation":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"__argc","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"__argv","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_mn","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"module_name"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_pkg","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"package"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_bt","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"build_type"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"s_kind","variable_type":"str","assignment_operation":"string","source_target":"kind"},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaratio